                      </b><br>
                      A man said to his wife one day, 'I don't know how
                      you can be so stupid and so beautiful all at the
                      same time.<br>
                      <br>
                      'The wife responded, 'Allow me to explain&#8230;<br>
                      <br>
                      God made me beautiful so you would be attracted to
                      me;<br>
                      <br>
                      God made me stupid so I would be attracted to you!</font><br>
